<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP for Password Reset</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="text-align: center;">OTP for Password Reset</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You recently requested to reset your password. To complete the process, please use the following One-Time
            Password (OTP):</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>If you did not request this password reset or believe it is a mistake, please ignore this email. Your
            password will remain unchanged.</p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 5 minutes. Please do not share this OTP with anyone.</p>
        <p>Thank you.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>